    v2 = wp.sin(wp.sin((tmp + 0.19 * v1 + 0.3)))
    v2 = 0.93
    v0 = wp.cos(v2)
    v1 = ((0.37 + wp.exp(v2 + 0.4)) + v2)
    data[tid] = v0
